long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Art-Fu helps to find you all creative resources you need in single place. Starting from stock audio,website templates,Facebook templates, Android and Flash game templates,WordPress themes,3D models,stock photos,stock motion video,plugins and much more.

If you are talented you might want to do research on items for sale and sign-up as exclusive author start selling own creations.

It's online version of old software Artist Market made long time ago.
